br />\n<br />\n政府消息人士指，學生資助處將於2018/19學年，向所有通過入息審查﹑領取全額或半額學生資助或來自綜援家庭的學生，每人派發$2000元。<br />\n<br />\n另外正領取「學費助學金、學習開支助學金及生活費貸款」（俗稱Grant Loan）的大專生，亦受惠每人獲派$2000。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2019855/財政預算案向37萬學生每人派-2000%E3%80%80邊類學生可獲津貼？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2019855%2F%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E5%90%9137%E8%90%AC%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%AF%8F%E4%BA%BA%E6%B4%BE-2000%25E3%2580%2580%E9%82%8A%E9%A1%9E%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%8F%AF%E7%8D%B2%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC%EF%BC%9F&d=YUUKqXhtvJWnT3ADY%2FvlnHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=799dcefd\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2019855/財政預算案向37萬學生每人派-2000%E3%80%80邊類學生可獲津貼？</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:22:03.000Z","msg":"依個plan洗唔洗自己申請？"},{"pid":"d0112d819b7d9b0259c1851dd721b744b651923f","tid":969971,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:24:14.000Z","msg":"借nonmean都有二千 屌啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da43ba8be01ab3f6f27cbd7829ca740ac9acdd5","tid":969971,"uid":77138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77bfe1fb449ef5d4fb16795f5630edbb8de23137","tid":969971,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T12:39:23.000Z","msg":"只須符合以下資格，便可申領4,000元：<br />\n<br />\n1. 年滿18歲<br />\n<br />\n2. 持香港身份證（包括新來港人士，但不包括來港工作、求學或接受培訓的香港非永久性居民及其受養人，也不包括以訪客身分來港的人士）<br />\n<br />\n3. 通常居住在香港（包括暫時離開香港而在合理預期情況下會返回香港居住的人士，例如因出差、留學或求醫而離港的香港居民，但不包括已移居海外的人士）<br />\n<br />\n4. 沒有受惠於2018-19年度《財政預算案》就綜合社會保障援助（綜援）、長者生活津貼、高齡津貼或傷殘津貼發放的額外兩個月款項<br />\n<br />\n5. 毋須繳交2017/18課稅年度的薪俸稅<br />\n<br />\n6. 在香港沒有物業<br />\n<br />\n貌似冇寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇可能唔拎綜援但有拎grant<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGrant 撚或成為最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"之前波叔咪話左個$2000無衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d7763eed886b2b84b266db0577dbd504dc500d","tid":969971,"uid":77138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"124269f19f98846f06103b41e47077c688a9d3ce","tid":969971,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff77063743d0234d2418b22e9b37a289ce1ee88f","tid":969971,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"799e3fc3bc44756201e57e0e3fcc43bef93b90fc","tid":969971,"uid":128164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:11:16.000Z","msg":"巴打講得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，係另一個計劃嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:12:23.000Z","msg":"夾埋拎8000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"無呀<br />\n都係6000<br />\n唔好ff<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f09d462d1676dc7cf40811ec0a9990232dcb3c6","tid":969971,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05d7763eed886b2b84b266db0577dbd504dc500d","tid":969971,"uid":77138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"124269f19f98846f06103b41e47077c688a9d3ce","tid":969971,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff77063743d0234d2418b22e9b37a289ce1ee88f","tid":969971,"uid":135445,"l